# Snyk Code (.dcignore) path exclusions
# Scopes Snyk Code (SAST) scanning to project-owned source files.
# Mirrors the exclude set in .snyk for consistency.
# See: docs/snyk-implementation-findings.md (Finding 1, Recommendation A)
.venv/
.worktrees/
node_modules/
site/
htmlcov/
out/
**/site-packages/**
